{"tid":1434402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家支持周柏豪","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:13:55.000Z","uid":27,"like":198,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"bc033c240934a43cbdfd3908cfa51fcd21aa0b5a","tid":1434402,"uid":27,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:33:23.000Z","msg":"佢為左香港人夠膽得罪大陸<br />\n仲要夠膽係微博發聲<br />\n由佢係係第一批為烈士悼念嘅Artist開始<br />\n我已經決定左<br />\n只要佢仲未唔做護旗手<br />\n我都唔會同佢割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日佢del ig嘅post del到16年嘅12月<br />\n可能係無聲抗議嘅一種 <br />\n我地唔知佢受嘅壓力有幾大<br />\n但如果我地輸左呢次抗爭<br />\n好似佢咁嘅願意發聲嘅藝人只會愈黎愈少<br />\n希望大家可以同柏豪 &ldquo;同行&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比周柏豪知道 香港仲有好多佢嘅同路人<br />\n唔好比佢獨自承受壓力<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n佢有首歌叫傑出青年<br />\n簡直可以做今次運動嘅主題曲<br />\n<br />\n#總是全情投入去<br />\n以誠意據理爭取<br />\n對邪惡會發聲姑息有罪<br />\n雖被指沉迷夢裡<br />\n惡型惡相欠規矩<br />\n恕難勸退我了解真理在誰#"},{"pid":"f79daec86fc9e91dcb7e9890af16ac8ad7dd641e","tid":1434402,"uid":119485,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5XqWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5XqWt.png&h=2edd738f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQGGSEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQGGSEb.jpg&h=f8cc4264&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dw1Dapa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDw1Dapa.jpg&h=f1f6aa56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKDJ5X5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKDJ5X5.jpg&h=efb6ebbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOSKQpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOSKQpb.jpg&h=e6dcca84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cm36bK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F